hadiths[140]{hadithnumber,text}:
2123,"Bishr-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Umara-bin-Ghaziya ne Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne marney waley logon ko) لا الہ الا اللہ ( ki talqeen karo."
2124,Abdul-Azeez darawardi aur Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne usi ( uper zikr ki gaee (sanad se ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
2125,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne marney waley logon ko) لا الہ الا اللہ ( ki talqeen karo."
2126,"Ismail-bin-Jafar ne kaha : mujhey Sad-bin-Saeed ne Umar-bin-kaseer-bin-aflah se khabar di, unhon-ne ( umr ( ibne- Safina se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : koi musalman nahi jisey museebat pahunchey aur wo ( wahi kuchh ( kahey jiska Allah ne usey hukm diya hai : yaqinan ham Allah ke hain aur usi ki taraf lotney waley hain, aey Allah ! mujhey meri museebat par ajr de aur mujhey ( iska (us se behtar badal ata farma magar Allah Taala usey us ( zaaye shuda cheez) ka behtar badal ata farma deta hai. ( Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : jab ( mere khawind ( abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to maine (dil mein) kaha : kon sa musalman abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se behtar (ho sakta ( hai ! wo pahlaa gharaana hai jisne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf hijrat ki. phir maine wo ( kalimaat ( kahey to Allah Taala ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sura mein iska badal ata farma diya. kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne liye nikah ka paigham detey huey Haatib-bin-abi Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) ko mere paas bheja to maine kaha : meri aik beti hai aur main bahut ghairat karne wali hun. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski beti ke barey mein ham Allah se dua kartey hain ke wo usko us (Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha)) se be niyaaz kar de aur main Allah se dua karta hun ke wo ( be-jaa ( ghairat ko (is se) hata de."
2127,"abu-Usama ne Sad-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-kaseer-bin-aflah ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine ibne- Safina se suna, wo bayan kar rahe they ke unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya ko ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : koi banda nahi jisey museebat pahunchey aur wo kahey : be-shak ham Allah ke hain aur usi ki taraf lotney waley hain. aey Allah ! mujhey meri museebat ka ajr de aur mujhey iska behtar badal ata farmaa. magar Allah Taala usey uski museebat ka ajr deta hai aur usey iska behtar badal ata farmata hai. (Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : to jab abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey, maine is tarah kaha jis tarah Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya tha to Allah Taala ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki suray mein unse behtar badal ata farma diya."
2128,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Sad-bin-Saeed ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-kaseer ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam ibne- Safina se khabar di aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna. padhi. ( aagey ( abu-Usama ki hadis ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki) aur ye izafa kiya : Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to maine (dil mein) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se behtar kon ho sakta hai? phir Allah Taala ne mere iraadey ko pukhta kar diya to maine wahi ( kalimaat ( kahey . iske baad meri Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shadi ho gaee."
2129,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mareez ya marney waley ke paas jao to bhalai ki baat kaho kyonke jo tum kehtey ho Farishtey is par Aameen kehtey hain. kaha : jab abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! abu-Salma wafat pa gaey hain. aap ne farmaya : tum (ye kalimaat ( kaho : aey Allah ! mujhey aur usko maaf farma aur iske baad mujhey iska behtreen badal ata farmaa. kaha : maine (ye kalimaat ( kahey to Allah Taala ne mujhey unke baad wo de diye jo mere liye unse behtar hain, yani Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)."
2130,"Abu-Ishaq-fazari ne Khalid-hazza se, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne qabeesa-bin-zuweb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif laaey, us waqt unki aankhen khuli huin thin to aap ne unhein band kar diya. phir farmaya : jab Rooh qabz ki jati hai to nazar uska peechha karti hai. is par unke ghar ke kuchh log chilla kar roney lagey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum apne liye bhalai ke ilawa aur koi dua na karo kyonke tum jo kehtey ho Farishtey is par Aameen kehtey hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki maghfirat farma, hidayat yaafta logon mein iske darjaat buland farma aur iske peechhey reh janey walon main to iska jaa-nasheen bin aur aey jahaanon ke paalne waley ! hamein aur isko bakhsh de, iske liye iski qabr mein kushadgi ata farma aur iske liye us ( qabr ( mein roshni kar de."
2131,"Ubaidullah-bin-Hasan ne kaha : hamein Khalid-Haza ne usi ( uper zikr ki gaee (sanad ke sath us (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, iske siwa ke unhon-ne ( ( واخلفه في عقبه ) ke bajaey) (واخلفه في تركته ) (jo kuchh us ne chhoda hai, yani ahal w maal , usmein iska jaa-nasheen bin ( kaha, aur unhon-ne ( اللهم ! اوسع له في قبره) (aey Allah ! uske liye uski qabr mein wusat paida farma ( kaha aur (افسح له  ) (aur us ke liye kushadgi paida farma ( nahi kaha aur) Ubaidullah ne) ye zayed bayan kya ke Khalid Haza ne kaha : aik aur saatwein dua ki jisey main bhool gaya."
2132,"ibne-Juraij ne Alaa-bin-Yaqoob se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum insan ko dekhtey nahi ke jab wo faut ho jata hai to uski nazar uth jati hai? logon ne kaha : kyon nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye us waqt hota hai jab uski nazar uski Rooh ka peechhaa karti hai."
2133,Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne ( bhi) Alaa se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( riwayat bayan ki.
2134,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : jab abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey, maine (dil mein) kaha : pardesii , pardes mein) faut ho gaya) main is par aisa ro'on gii ke iska khub charcha hoga. chunanche maine is par roney ki taiyaarii kar li ke achcha oopri ilaaqey se aik aurat aai. wo ( roney mein) mera sath dena chahti thi ke usey samney se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mil gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum shaitan ko is ghar main ( dobara ( dakhil karna chahti ho, jahan se Allah ne usko nikal diya hai? do baar (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kalimaat kahey ( to main roney se ruk gaee aur na rooii ."
2135,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Aasim ahwal se, unhon-ne abu-Usmaan nehdi se aur unhon-ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke aap ki betiyon mein se aik ne aapko bulatey huey aur itlaa detey huey aap ki taraf paigham bheja ke uska bachcha. ya uska betaa maut (ke aalim ( mein hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne payaam laney waley se farmaya : unke paas wapas ja kar unko bataao ke Allah hi ka hai jo usney ley liya aur usi ka hai. jo usney diya tha aur uske yahaan har cheez ka waqt muqarrar hai, aur unko bata do ke wo sabr karein aur ajr w sawab ki talabgar hun. payaam rasaan dobara aaya aur kaha : unhon-ne ( aapko ( qism di hai ke aap unke paas zaroor tashrif laaein . kaha : is par Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur aap ke sath Hazrat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi uth khadey huey aur main bhi unke sath chal padaa. aap ke samney bachchey ko pesh kiya gaya jabke iska saans ukhdaa hua tha, ( jism is tarah muztarib tha) jaisey iski jaan puraaney mishkeezey mein ho to aap ki aankhen bah padiin. is par Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ye kya hai? aap ne farmaya : ye rehmat hai jo Allah ne apne bandon ke dilon mein rakhi hai aur Allah apne bandon mein se raham dil bandon hi par raham farmata hai."
2136,"ibne- Fuzel aur abu-Muawiya har aik ne Aasim ahwal se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) ( hadis bayan ki, albatta Hammad ki hadis zyada mukammal aur zyada lambi hai."
2137,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) apni bimari mein mubtala huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) , Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) , aur Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath unki iyaadat ke liye unke paas tashrif ley gaey. jab aap unke yahaan dakhil huey to unhein ghashii ki haalat mein paya. aap ne puchha : kya unhon-ne apni muddat poori kar li ( wafat pa gaey hain) ? logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! nahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ro padey , jab logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rotey huey dekha to unhon-ne bhi ronaa shuru kar diya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kiya tum suno gey nahi ke Allah Taala aankh ke aansu aur dil ke gham par saza nahi deta balke is ''aap ne apni zaban Mubarak ki taraf ishara kya''  ki wjah se azab deta hai ya raham karta hai."
2138,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they ke Ansar mein se aik aadmi aaya, us ne aapko salam kaha aur phir wo Ansari pusht pher kar chal diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Ansar ke bhai ( Ansari ( ! mere bhai Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ka kya haal hai? usne kaha : wo achchha hai. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kon uski iyaadat karega? phir aap uthey aur aap ke sath ham bhi uth khadey huey. ham das se zayed log they, hamarey paas jootey na they na mozey , na topiyaan aur na qamees hii. ham is shoreelii zamin par chaltey huey unke paas pahunch gaey, unki qaum ke log unke ird-gird se peechhey hat gaey yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) jo aap ke sath they, (unke ( qareeb ho gaey."
2139,"Muhammad yani Jafar (sadiq) ke farzand ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Sabit se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sabr pahley sadmey ke waqt hai (iske baad to insan gham ko ahista-ahista bardasht karne lagta hai.)"
2140,Usman-bin-Umar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Sabit Bunani ke hawale se Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik aurat ke paas aaey jo apne bachchey (ki maut ( par ro rahi thi to aap ne unse farmaya : Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karo aur sabr karo usne kaha : aapko meri museebat ki kya parwaa? jab aap chaley gaey to usko bataya gaya ke wo ( tumhen sabr ki talqeen karne waale) Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they. to us aurat par maut jaisi kaifiyat taarii ho gaee. wo aap ke darwazey par aai to usne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwazey par darbaan na paaey. usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine (us waqt) aapko nahi pehchaana tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (haqiqi) sabr pahley sadmey ya sadmey ke shuruat hi mein hota hai.
2141,"Khalid-bin-Haaris, Abdul-Malik bin-Amr , aur Abdus-Samad sab ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath Usman-bin-Umar ke sunaaiye gaey waqiey ke mutabiq uski hadis ki tarah hadis sunai aur Abdus-Samad ki hadis mein (ye jumla ( hai : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabar ke paas ( baithi hui ( aik aurat ke paas se guzrey."
2142,"Naafe ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Umar ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) saiyede-naa umr (Raziallahu anhu) (ki haalat ( par roney lagiin to unhon-ne kaha : aey meri beti ! ruk jao kya tumhen malum nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : maiyat ko is par uske ghar walon ki aah w bakaa se azab diya jata hai ."
2143,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada ko Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : maiyat ko uski qabr main is par kiye janey waley nauhey se azab diya ja ta hai."
2144,"Saeed (bin abi-Aruba ( ne Qatada se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : maiyat ko uski qabr main is par kiye janey waley nauhey se azab diya jata hai."
2145,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi kiya gaya wo be-hosh ho gaey tab un par buland awaz se cheekh w pukar ki gaee jab unko fayda hua to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum log jantey nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maiyat ko zinda ke roney se azab diya jata hai?"
2146,"(Abu-Is'haq ( Shebani ne abu-Burda se aur unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi kiya gaya to Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kehna shuru kar diya : haaye mera bhai ! to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : Suheb ! kya tumhen malum nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zinda ke roney se maiyat ko azab diya jata hai?"
2147,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne abu-Burda-bin-abi Musa se aur unhon-ne (apne walid (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi huey to Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar se aaey yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas andar dakhil huey aur unke samney khadey ho kar roney lagey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : kyon ro rahe ho? kya mujh par ro rahe ho? kaha : Allah ki qism ! haan , ameerul-momeneen ! aap hi par ro raha hun. to unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! tumhen khub ilm hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha jis par aah w bakaa ki jaey usey azab diya jata hai. ( abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne) kaha : maine ye hadis Musa-bin-Talha ke samney bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kaha karti thin (ye ( yahudiyon ka mamla tha. ( dekhiye hadis number 2153 .)"
2148,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi kar diya gaya to Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne un par vavela kiya. unhon-ne kaha : aey Hafsa ! kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey nahi suna ke jis par vavela kiya ja ta hai usey azab diya jata hai? aur (usi tarah) Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi vaela kiya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Suheb ! kya tumhen ilm nahi : jis par vavela kiya jaey usko azab diya jata hai?
2149,"Ayub ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Muleka se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke pahlu mein betha hua tha. ham Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi Umme- Aban ke janazey ka intizar kar rahe they jabke Amr-bin-Usman bhi unke paas they itney mein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aaey unhein lekar aaney wala aik aadmi laya mere khayal mein us ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baithney ki jagah ke barey mein bataya to wo aa kar mere pahlu mein baith gaey mein un donon ke darmyan mein tha achcha ghar (ke andar ( se ( roney ki) awaz aai to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne. aur aisa lagta tha wo Amr (bin-Usman) ko ishara kar rahe hain ke wo uthein aur unko rokein. kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai bila shubah maiyat ko iske ghar walon ke ro ne se azab diya jata hai. ( Abdullah-bin-Ubai Muleka ne) kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko bila shart w qaid (yani har tarah ke ro ne ke hawale se) bayan kiya. is par Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ameer-ul-mou-mineen Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they yahan tak ke jab ham beda ke maqam par pahunchey to unhon-ne aik aadmi ko darakht ke saaey mein padao daley dekha unhon-ne mujh se kaha : jao aur mere liye pata karo ke wo kon aadmi hai main gaya to dekha wo Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) they mein unke paas wapas aaya aur kaha : aap ne mujhey hukm diya tha ke main aap ke liye pata karun ke wo kon shakhs hain to wo Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) hain. unhon-ne kaha : ( jao aur) unko hukm (pahuncha) do ke wo hamarey sath ( qafley mein) aa jaaein. maine kaha : unke sath unke ghar waley hain unhon-ne kaha : chahey unke sath unke ghar waley ( bhi) hain ( shamil ho jayen ). kabhi-kabhi Ayub ne ( bas yahan tak kaha ( unse kaho ke wo hamarey sath ( qafley mein) shamil ho jaaein.   ...jab ham Madina pahunchey to zyada waqt na guzra tha ke ameer-ul-mou-mineen  zakhmi kar diye gaey Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ye kehtey huey aaey haaye mera bhai ! haaye mera sathi ! to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kya tumhen malum nahi ya (kaha : tum ne suna nahi. padhi. Ayub ne kaha : ya unhon-ne (iske bajaey)  kya tumhen pata nahi aur tum ne suna nahi ke alfaz kahey . ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maiyat ko iske ghar walon ke kuchh ( tarah ke) roney se azab diya jata hai) ibne-abi-Mulaika ne) kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne us ( roney ke lafz ( ko bila qaid bayan kiya. jabke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( lafz ( kuchh (ki qaid (ke sath kaha tha. main ( ibne-abi-Mulaika ( uth kar Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo kaha tha unko bataya unhon-ne kaha nahi Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kabhi nahi farmaya ke maiyat ko kisi aik ke roney ki wjah se azab diya jata hai balke aap ne farmaya hai : Allah Taala kaafir ke azab mein iske ghar walon ke ro ne ki wjah se izafa kar deta hai (kyonke kafiron ne apni aulad ko buland awaz se ronaa sikhaya hota hai raha baghair awaz ke ronaa to uski zimme-dari roney waley par nahi kyonke ( be-shak Allah hi hai jisne hansaayaa aur rulaayaa aur bojh uthaney wali koi jaan kisi dusri ka bojh nahi uthaey gii .) awaz ke baghair mahz aansuon se roney ka na roney waley ko gunah hai na iske badon ko kyonke wo bhi iske zimme daar nahi.) Ayub ne kaha : ibne-abi-Mulaika ne kahan mujh se Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kiya unhon-ne kaha : jab Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko Hazrat umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)  ki ye baat pahunchi to unhon-ne kaha : tum mujhey aisey do afraad ki hadis bayan kartey ho jo na ( khud ( jhoot bolney waley hain aur na jhutlaaey janey waley hain lekin) kabhi-kabhi ( samaa, ( sunnaa ( ghalat ho jata hai (kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aur siyaaq mein ye baat ki thi dekhiye hadis number 2153 , 2156 ( . padhi."
2150,ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Ubai Muleka ne khabar di unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi Makka mein fout ho gaee to ham unke janazey mein shirkat ke liye aaey Hazrat ibne-Umar aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi tashrif laey. mein un donon ke darmyan mein betha tha. main unmein se aik ke paas betha tha phir doosra aa kar mere pahlu mein baith gaya. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Amr-bin-Usman se aur wo unke ru-baro baithey huey they kaha : tum ro ne se roktey kyon nahi ? be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha maiyat ko iske ghar walon ke is par roney se azab diya jata hai. is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) iske kuchh ( kuchh tarah ke roney se) kaha kartey they phir unhon-ne ( mukammal ( hadis bayan ki kaha : main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka se lota yahan tak ke jab ham maqam beda par pahunchey to achcha unhein darakht ke saaey taley kuchh oont sawar dikhai diye unhon-ne kaha : ja kar dekho ye oont sawar kon hain? maine dekha to wo Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) they maine ( aa kar) unhein bataya to unhon-ne kaha : unhein mere paas bulao . main lot kar Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya. maine kaha : chaliye ameerul-momeneen ke sath ho jaaiye iske baad jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi kar diye gaey to Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) rotey huey andar aaey keh rahe they haaye mera bhai ! haaye mera sathi ! to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Suheb ! kya tum mujh par ro rahe ho? halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai : maiyat ko iske ghar walon ke kuchh ( tarah ke) roney se azab diya jata hai. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaey to maine ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : Allah umr (Raziallahu anhu) par raham farmaai ! Allah ki qism ! nahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya ke Allah Taala momin ko kisi ke roney ki wjah se azab deta hai. balke aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala kafir ke azab ko iske ghar walon ke is par roney ki wjah se badha deta hai. kaha aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aur tumharey liye Quran kafi hai (jis mein ye hai) aur bojh uthaney wali koi jaan kisi dusri jaan ka bojh nahi uthaey gii . uskey sath Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur Allah hi hansaataa hai aur rulaa ta hai. ibne-abi-Mulaika ne ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( jawab mein) kuchh nahi kaha.
2151,"Amr (bin-Dinar ( ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi umme Aban ke janazey main ( hazir ( they. aur mazkura (uper zikr) hadis bayan ki, unhon ( Amr ( ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se ( aagey ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat marfoo honey ki sarahat nahi ki jis tarah Ayub aur ibne-Juraij ne uski sarahat ki hai aur un donon ki hadis Amr ki hadis se zyada mukammal hai."
2152,Salim ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maiyat ko zinda ke roney se azab diya jata hai.
2153,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke samney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka riwayat ki hui qaul bayan kiya gaya : maiyat ko iske ghar walon ke roney se azab diya jata hai to unhon-ne kaha : Allah Abdur-Rehman par raham farmaai unhon-ne aik cheez ko suna lekin) poori tarah) mehfooz na rakha (sachha waaqea' ye hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik Yahudi ka janaaza guzra aur wo log is par ro rahe they, to aap ne farmaya : tum ro rahe ho aur usey azab diya ja raha hai."
2154,abu-Usama ne Hisham se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas is baat ka zikr kiya gaya ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan ye bayan kartey hain : maiyat ko uski qabr mein iske ghar walon ke roney se azab diya jata hai. unhon-ne kaha : wo ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) bhool gaey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to ye farmaya tha is ( marney waale) ko uski ghalati ya gunah ki wjah se azab diya ja raha hai aur uske ghar waley ab usi waqt is par ro rahe hain aur ye ( bhool ( un ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) ki is riwayat ki tarah hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badr ke din us kuwein (ke kinarey ( par khadey huey jis badr mein qatl hone-waale mushrikon ki laashein thin. to aap ne unse jo kehna tha kaha (aur farmaya : ab ( jo main keh raha hun wo usko b-khoobii sun rahe hain. halanke (is baat mein bhi) wo bhool gaey aap ne to farmaya tha : ye log b-khoobii jantey hain ke main unse ( duniya mein) jo kaha karta tha wo haq tha. phir unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne (ye aayatein padhein (aur be-shak to mardon ko nahi suna sakta. aur to hargiz unhein sunaney wala nahi jo qabron mein hain ( maano (aap ye keh rahe hain : jabke wo aag mein apne thikaaney bana chukey hain. (aur wo achi tarah jaan chukey hain ke jo unse kaha gaya tha wahi sach hai yani ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) un do riwayaton ka asl bayan mehfooz nahi rakh sakey. (
2155,Wakee ne bayan kiya ke hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne isi sanad se abu-Usama ki hadis ke ham mana hadis sunai aur abu-Usama ki) uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis zyada mukammal hai.
2156,Umra-binte-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna (us mauqe par) unke samney bayan kiya gaya tha Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain maiyat ko zinda ke roney ki wjah se azab diya jata hai to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah abu Abdur-Rehman ko maaf farmaai ! yaqinan unhon-ne jhoot nahi bola lekin wo bhool gaey hain ya unse ghalati ho gaee hai) sachha waaqea' ye hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik Yahudi aurat (ke janazey (ke paas se guzrey jis par aah w bakaa ki ja rahi thi to aap ne farmaya : ye log is par ro rahe hain aur usko uski qabr mein azab diya ja raha hai.
2157,"Wakee ne Saeed-bin-Ubaid Tai aur Muhammad-bin-Qais se aur unhon-ne Ali-bin Rabee se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Kufa mein sabse pahley jis par nauha kya gaya wo qarza-bin-Kab tha is par Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai. jis par nauha kiya gaya usey qiyamat ke din is par kiye janey waley nauhey (ki wjah ( se azab diya jaeyga"
2158,"hamein Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( hamein Muhammad-bin-Qais ne Ali-bin-Rabee se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki."
2159,Marwan-bin-Muawiya fazari ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Ubaid taai ne Ali-bin-Rabee se hadis sunai unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki.
2160,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein jaahliyat ke kaamon mein se char baatein ( maujood ( hain wo unko tark nahi karengey ahsaab ( bap dada ke aslii ya ghadey hue naamon ( par fakhr karna, ( dusron ke) nasb par ta'ana karna, sitaron ke zariey se barish maangna aur nauha karna aur farmaya nauha karne wali jab apni maut se pahley tauba na karey to qiyamat ke din usko us haalat mein uthaya jaeyga ke us (ke badan ( par taarkol ka libaas aur khaarish ki qamees hogi."
2161,"Abdul Wahab ne kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna wo keh rahe they mujhey Umra ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo farma rahi thin jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Zaid-bin-Haarisa, Jafar-bin-abii-Taalib aur Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ke qatl ( Shahid ( honey ki khabar pahunchi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah (masjid mein) baithey ke aap (ke chehra anwar ( par gham ka pata chal raha tha. kaha : main darwazey ki jhurii, darwazey ki darz  se dekh rahi thi ke aap ke paas aik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Jafar (ke khandan ( ki auratein. aur us ne unke roney ka tazkira kiya aap ne usey hukm diya ke wo ja kar unhein rokey wo chala gaya wo ( dobara (aap ke paas aaya aur bataya ke unhon-ne uski baat nahi maana aap ne usey dobara hukm diya ke wo ja kar unhein rokey wo gaya aur phir ( teesri baar (aap ke paas aa kar kehney laga : Allah ki qism ! Allah ke rasool! wo ham par ghalib aa gaee hain. kaha : un ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao aur unke munh mein mitti daal do. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine (dil mein) kaha : Allah teri naak khaak aalud karey ! Allah ki qism ! na tum wo kaam kartey ho jiska Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen hukm diya hai aur na hi tum ne ( baar-baar bata kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef ( dena ( tark kiya hai."
2162,"Abdullah-bin-Numair , Muawiya-bin-Saleh aur Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muslim ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se is sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki aur Abdul-Azeez ki hadis mein hai tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mashaqqat mein dalney se baaz nahi aaey."
2163,"Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bait ke sath ham se ye ahad liya ke ham nauha nahi karengii to ham mein se un panch aurton : Umme-Sulaim , Umme- Alaa abu sabra ki beti , Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ya abu sabra ki beti aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ke siwa kisi ne (jaisa ki haq tha) uski paasdaarii nahi ki."
2164,"Hisham ne Hafsa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bait mein ham se ye ahad liya ke tum nauha nahi karo gii ham mein se panch ke siwa kisi ne uski (jaisa ki haq tha) paasdaarii nahi ki, un ( panch ( mein se aik Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
2165,"Aasim ne Hafsa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ye aayat nazil hui : auratein aap se bait karein ke wo Allah Taala ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thehraein gii . aur kisi nek kaam mein aap ki mukhalifat nahi karengii . kaha is ( ahad ( mein se aik nauha girii  bhi thi to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! falan khandan ke siwa kyonke unhon-ne jaahliyat ke daur main ( nauha karne par) mere sath ta'awun kiya tha to ab mere liye bhi la-zamii hai ke main (eik baar ( unke sath ta'awun karun. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : falan ke khandan ke siwa ."
2166,Muhammad-bin-Sirin ne kaha : Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya hamein janaazon ke sath janey se rokaa jata tha lekin hamein sakhti ke sath hukm nahi diya gaya.
2167,"Hafsa ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein janaazon ke sath janey se rokaa gaya lekin hamein sakhti ke sath hukm nahi diya gaya."
2168,"Yazeed-bin-Zaree ne Ayub se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi ko ghusl de rahi thin to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aap ne farmaya : usko teen, panch ya agar tumhari raey ho to us se zayed martaba pani aur berii (ke patton ( se ghusl do aur aakhiri baar mein kafaur ya kafaur main se kuchh daal dena aur jab tum farigh ho jao to mujhey itilaa  kar dena. jab ham farigh ho gain to ham ne aapko itlaa'  di to aap ne hamein apna tehband diya aur farmaya : usko iske jism ke sath lapet do."
2169,"Hafsa-binte-Sirin ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne un (ke baalon ( ki kanghi karke teen gundhii hui latein bana dein."
2170,"Malik-bin-Anas , Hammad aur ibne-Ulaih ne Ayub se unhon-ne Muhammad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki betiyon mein se aik wafat pa gain . ibne-Ulaih ki hadis main ( yun ( hai) umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur ham aap ki beti ko ghusl de rahi thin aur Malik ki hadis mein hai kaha : jab aap ki beti wafat pa gain to aap hamarey paas tashrif laey. padhi. (is se aagey ( umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se Muhammad , unse Ayub aur unse Yazeed ki hadis ki tarah hai."
2171,"Hammad ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Hafsa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, iske siwa ke aap ne farmaya : teen , panch, saat (7) ya agar tumhari raey ho to us se zayed baar (ghusl dena). Hafsa ne umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ham ne unke sar (ke baalon ( ki teen gundhii hui latein bana dein."
2172,"(Ismail ( ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Hafsa ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se ( bayan kartey huey) kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : usko taaq tadaad mein teen , panch ya saat (7) martaba ghusl do. kaha aur umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne un (ke baalon ( ki kanghi karke teen chuttiyen bana dein."
2173,Aasim ahwal ne Hafsa-binte-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) badi ( beti Zenab (Raziallahu anha) wafat pa gain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein farmaya : usey taaq tadaad mein teen ya panch martaba ghusl do aur paanchwein baar (pani mein) kafaur  ya kuchh kafaur  daal dena aur jab tum ghusl se farigh ho jao to mujhey batanaa. ham ne aapko bataya to aap ne hamein apna tehband diya aur farmaya : is ( tehband ( ko iske jism ke sath lapet do.
2174,"Hisham-bin-Hassan ne Hafsa-binte-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur ham aap ki betiyon mein se aik ko ghusl de rahi thin to aap ne farmaya : usey taaq tadaad mein panch ya us se zayed baar ghusl dena. ( aagey ( Ayub aur Aasim ki hadis ke ham mana ( hadis bayan ki) us hadis mein unhon-ne kaha : ( umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ham ne unke baalon ko teen tihaaiyon mein gundh diya. unke sar ke donon taraf aur unki peshani ke baal ."
2175,Hashim ne Khalid se khabar di unhon-ne Hafsa-bint-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jahan unhein apni beti ko ghusl dene ka hukm diya to ( wahan ye bhi) farmaya : unki daain taraf se aur uske wuzu ke ang (اعضا ء) se. (ghusl ki shuruaat karo. (
2176,Ismail ibne-Ulaih ne Khalid se unhon-ne Hafsa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beti ke ghusl ke barey mein unse farmaya : unki daain taraf se aur unke wuzu ke aaza se shuruat karo.
2177,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se unhon-ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Khabbaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Allah ke rastey mein hijrat ki. ham Allah ki raza chaahatey they. to (uske waadey ke mutabiq ( hamara ajr Allah par wajib ho gaya. ham mein se kuchh log chaley gaey unhon-ne ( duniya mein) apne ajr mein se kuchh nahi liya unmein se aik Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) they wo Uhud ke din Shahid huey to unke liye aik dhaarii daar chadar ke siwa koi cheez na mili jis mein unko kafan diya jata. jab ham usko unke sar par daltey to unke paon bahar nikal jatey aur jab ham usey unke pairon par rakhtey to sar nikal jata. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usko unke sar waley hissey par daal do aur paon par kuchh izkhir ( ghaas ( daal do aur ham mein se koi aisa hai jiske liye phal paak chuka hai aur wo usko chun raha hai ."
2178,"Jareer, Esa-bin-Yonus Ali-bin-Mus'hir aur ibne-Uena ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
2179,abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sahool ( Yaman ( se laey janey waley teen safaid soti kapdon mein kafan diya gaya unmein na qamees thi aur na amama albatta hulley ( ham rang chaadaron par mushtamil jodey (ke hawale se log ishtibaah mein pad gaey bila shubah wo aap ke liye khareeda  gaya tha taake aapko usmein kafan diya jaey. phir us hulley ko chhod diya gaya aur aapko sahool ki teen safaid kapdon mein kafan diya gaya aur us ( hulley ( ko Abdullah-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ley liya aur kaha : main usko (apne paas ( mehfooz rakhoonga yahan tak ke usmein khud apne kafan ka intizam karunga baad mein kaha : agar usko Allah Taala apne Nabi ke liye pasand farmata to aapko usmein kafan ( dene ka bando-bast kar) deta isliye unhon-ne usey farokht kar diya aur uski qeemat sadqa kar di.
2180,Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se hadis sunai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Abdullah-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik yamnii hulley mein lapeta (kafan-diyaa) gaya phir usko utaar diya gaya aur aapko sahool ke teen safaid yamnii kapdon mein kafan diya gaya. jin mein na qamees thi aur na amama . Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo hulla utha liya aur kaha : mujhey usmein kafan diya jaeyga phir kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usmein kafan nahi diya gaya to mujhey usmein kafan diya jaeyga ! chunanche unhon-ne usko sadqa kar diya.
2181,"Hafs-bin-Ghiyas , ibne-Uena , ibne-Idrees , Abda , Wakee aur Abdul-Azeez sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur unki hadis mein Abdullah-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ka waqia nahi hai."
2182,abu-Salma ( Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya : maine unse kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kitney kapdon mein kafan diya gaya tha? to unhon-ne kaha : teen sahooli kapdon mein.
2183,"Saleh (bin-kaisaan ( ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se riwayat ki, unhein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) faut huey to aapko dhaarii daar yamnii chadar se dhaa-napaa gaya."
2184,Mamar aur Shuaib ne ( ibne-Shahab ( Zohri se isi sanad ke sath bilkul isi tarah hadis riwayat ki.
2185,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke aik din Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya, aap ne apne ashaab mein se aik aadmi ka tazkira farmaya jo faut hua to usko maamooli ( kapdey mein) kafan diya gaya aur raat hi ko dafn kar diya gaya to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi bhi aadmi ko raat ko dafn karne se daant kar rokaa yahan tak ke uski ( shaan shaayaan tareeqey se) namaaze-janaaza ada ki jaey siwaae iske ke koi insan is par majbur ho jaey aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai ko kafan de to usey achchha kafan de."
2186,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se unhon-ne Saeed (bin-Musaiyab) se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya: janazey (ko ley janey ( mein jaldi karo, agar wo ( maiyat ( nek hai to jiski taraf tum usko ley ja rahe ho wo khair hai agar wo iske siwa hai to phir wo shar hai jisey tum apni gardanon se utaar doge."
2187,"Mamar aur Muhammad-bin-abi Hafsa donon ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed (bin-Musaiyab ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( yahi hadis) riwayat ki, lekin Mamar ki hadis mein hai unhon-ne kaha : main iske siwa aur kuchh nahi janta ke unhon ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) ne us hadis ko marfoo ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) bayan kiya hai."
2188,abu-Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : janazey mein jaldi karo agar ( maiyat ( nek hai to tum ne usey bhalai ke qareeb kar diya aur agar wo iske siwa hai to shar hai jisey tum apni gardanon se utaar doge.
2189,"abu-Taahir Hurmala-bin-Yahya aur Haaroon-bin-Saeed eilii ....  is riwayat ke alfaz Harun aur Hurmala ke hain. padhi. mein se Harun ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai aur doosrey donon ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Hurmuz Aaraj ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs janazey mein Sharik raha yahan tak ke namaaze-janaaza ada kar li gaee to uske liye aik qirat hai. aur jo us ( janazey ( mein Sharik raha yahan tak ke usko dafn kar diya gaya to uske liye do qirat hain. puchha gaya : do qirat se kya murad hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do badey pahadon ki tarah . abu-Taahir ki hadis yahan khatm ho gaee. doosrey do asaatza ne izafa kya : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne kaha : ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) namaaze-janaaza padh kar lot aatey they jab unko Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis pahunchi to unhon-ne kaha yaqinan ham ne bahut se qeeraaton mein nuqsan uthaya ."
2190,"Abdul-Aala aur abdur razzaq ne Mamar se unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (ye riwayat ( un alfaz : do azeem pahadon tak bayan ki aur uske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kiya aur Abdul-Aala ki hadis mein hai. yahan tak ke us (ke dafn) se faarigh ho jaey. aur Abdur-Razzaq ki hadis mein hai : yahan tak ke usko lahad mein rakh diya jaey."
2191,Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : mujhey kai logon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jis tarah Mamar ki hadis hai aur kaha : aur jo usko dafn kiye janey tak iske sath raha.
2192,"Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : jisne namaaze-janaaza ada ki aur uske peechhey (qabristaan) nahi gaya to uske liye aik qirat (ajr) hai aur agar wo iske peechhey gaya to uske liye do qirat hain. puchha gaya : do qirat kya hain? farmaya : un donon mein se chhota Uhud pahaad ki tarah hai."
2193,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jisne namaaze-janaaza ada ki to uske liye qirat hai aur jo iske sath gaya yahan tak ke usey qabr mein utaar diya gaya to (iske liye) do qirat hain. (abu-Hazim ne) kaha maine kaha : aey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) qirat kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : Uhud pahaad ki tarah."
2194,Naafe ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jo shakhs janazey ke peechhey chala to uske liye aik qirat ajr hai. is par ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein kasarat se hadison sunai hain iske baad unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas paigham bheja aur unse puchha to unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki tasdeeq farmai is par Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : yaqinan ham ne bahut se qeeraaton (ko hasil karne) mein kotahi ki.
2195,Dawood-bin-Aamir-bin-Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ne apne walid (Aamir) se hadis bayan ki ke wo Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they ke sahib maqsoora Khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aa kar kaha : aey Abdullah-bin-Umar ! kya aap ne nahi suna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kya kehtey hain? bila shubah unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai. jo shakhs janazey ke sath uske ghar se nikla aur uski namaaze-janaaza ada ki phir uske sath raha yahan tak ke usko dafn kar diya gaya to uske liye bataur ajr do qirat hain har qirat ahad ( pahaad ( ki tarah hai aur jisne uski namaaze-janaaza ada ki aur lot aaya iska ajr Uhud pahaad jaisa hai (ye baat sun kar) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bheja (taake ( wo unse Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaul ke barey mein malum karein aur phir wapas aa kar unko bataein ke unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kya kaha? (is doran mein) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne masjid ki kankariyon se aik muththii bhar li aur unko apne hath mein ulat palat karne lagey yahan tak ke payaam rasaan unke paas wapas aa gaya usne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha hai ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne sach kaha hai is par ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo kankariyaan jo unke hath mein thin zamin par de maarein phir kaha yaqinan ham ne bahut se qeeraaton (ko hasil karne) mein kotahi ki.
2196,Shoba ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad se hadis sunai unhon-ne Madaan ibne-abi-Talha Yamari se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne namaaze-janaaza padhi uske liye aik qirat hai aur agar wo iske dafn mein shamil hua to uske liye do qirat hain (eik ( qirat ahad ( pahaad ( ki tarah hai.
2197,Hisham Saeed aur Aban ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath pichhli hadis ki tarah riwayat ki Saeed aur Hisham ki hadis mein hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se qirat ke barey mein malum kiya gaya to aap ne farmaya : ahad ( pahaad ( ki tarah.
2198,"Salaam-bin-abi mutee' ne Ayub se unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke doodh Sharik bhai Abdullah-bin-Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi) musalman ( marney wala jiski namaaze-janaaza musalmanon ki aik jamat jinki tadaad sou tak pahunchi ho, ada karey wo sab uski sifarish karein to iske barey mein unki sifarish qabool kar li jati hai. (salam ne) kaha maine ye hadis Shuaib-bin-habhaab ko bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi ye hadis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki."
2199,"Haron-bin-Maruf, Haaroon-bin-Saeed eilii aur Waleed-bin-shujaa' mein se Waleed ne kaha : mujhey hadis sunai aur doosrey donon ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai ibne- Wahab ne unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-sakhr ne Shareek-bin-Abdullaah-bin-abii-Namir se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke qudaid ya Asfan mein unke aik betey ka intiqal ho gaya to unhon-ne kaha : Kureb ! dekho iske ( janazey ke) liye kitney log jama ho chukey hain. main baahar nikla to dekha ke uski khaatir ( khaasey ( log jama ho chukey hain to maine unko itlaa'  di. unhon-ne puchha tum kehtey ho ke wo chalis (40) hongey ? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan. to unhon-ne farmaya : is ( maiyat ( ko) ghar se) bahar nikaalo kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : jo bhi musalman faut ho jata hai aur uske janazey par) aisey ( chalis (40) aadmi (namaz ada karne ke liye) khadey ho jatey hain jo Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi thehratey to Allah Taala iske barey mein unki sifarish ko qabool farma leta hai. ibne- Maruf ki riwayat mein hai unhon-ne Sharik-bin-abi-namr se unhon-ne Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. (is sanad mein Sharik ke walid aur abu namr ke betey Abdullah ka naam liye baghair dada ki taraf mansub kartey huey Sharik-bin-abi-namr kaha gaya hai.)"
2200,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Suhaib ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik janaaza guzra to uski achi sifat bayan ki gaee is par Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee. iske baad aik aur janaaza guzra to uski buri sifat bayan ki gaee to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee. is par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap par mere maan-baap fidaa hon ! aik janaaza guzra aur uski achi sifat bayan ki gaee to aap ne farmaya : wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee. aik aur janaaza guzra aur uski buri sifat bayan ki gaee to aap ne farmaya wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee, wajib ho gaee ( iska matlab kya hai? ). to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiski tum logon ne achi sifat bayan ki uske liye jannat wajib ho gaee aur jiski tum ne buri sifat bayan ki uske liye aag wajib ho gaee tum zamin mein Allah ke gawah ho, tum zamin mein Allah ke gawah ho, tum zamin mein Allah ke gawah ho."
2201,Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se aik janaaza guzra . iske baad unhon-ne Anas se Abdul-Azeez ki (pichhli ( hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki albatta Abdul-Azeez ki hadis zyada mukammal hai.
2202,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Halhala se, unhon-ne Mabad-bin-Kab-bin-Malik se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Qatada-bin-Rabaii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se aik janaaza guzra to aap ne farmaya : aaraam paaney wala hai ya us se aaraam milney wala hai. unhon ( sahaba ( ne puchha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aaraam paaney wala ya jis se aaraam milney wala hai se kya murad hai? to aap ne farmaya : banda momin duniya ki takaalif se aaraam paata hai aur faajir bandey (ke marney ( se log, Shahar, darakht aur haiwaanaat aaraam patey hain."
2203,Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Abdur-Razzaq ne Abdullah-bin-Saeed se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Amr se unhon-ne Kab-bin-Malik ke betey ( Mabad ( se unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( riwayat bayan ki aur Yahya ki hadis mein hai : wo ( momin banda ( Allah ki rehmat mein aa kar duniya ki azeeyat aur thakaan se aaraam hasil kar leta hai.
2204,"Imam Malik-ne-ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jis din Najashi faut huey. logon ko unki wafat ki itlaa di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) (ke sath bahar janaaza gaah mein gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char takbeerein kahin."
2205,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Habsha waley ( hukmaraan ( Najashi ki, jis din wo faut huey, maut ki khabar di aur farmaya : apne bhai ke liye bakhshish ki dua karo. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne hadis sunai ke unko Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne janaaza gaah mein unki safain banwaaein , Namaz ( janaaza ( padhai aur is par char takbeerein kahin."
2206,Saleh ne donon sanadon ke sath ibne-Shahab se Aqeel (bin-Khalid ( ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat ki.
2207,Saeed-bin-Mina ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne as'hama Najashi ki namaaze-janaaza ada ki to is par char takbeerein kahin .
2208,"Ata ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj Allah ka aik nek banda as'hama faut ho gaya hai. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey, hamari imamat karaai aur uski namaaze-janaaza ada ki."
2209,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah tumhara aik bhai wafat pa gaya hai, lihaza tum log utho aur is par Namaz (janaaza) padho .) Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : is par ham uthey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari do safain banaaein ."
2210,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Ali-bin hijr , aur Yahya-bin-Ayub ne kaha : hamein Ismail-ibne-Ulaih ne Ayub se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu-Muhallab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhara aik bhai wafat pa gaya hai lihaza tum utho aur uski namaaze-janaaza ada karo. aap ki murad Najashi se thi aur Zuhair ki riwayat main (un اخالكم ( (tumhara aik bhai ki bajaey) (un اخاكم ( ) tumhara bhai (ke alfaz hain."
2211,"Hasan-bin- Rabe aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Shebani se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Shabi se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maiyat ke dafn kiye janey ke baad aik qabr par namaaze-janaaza padhi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par char takbeerein kahin . Shebani ne kaha : maine Shabi se puchha : aapko ye hadis kis ne bayan ki? unhon-ne kaha : aik qaabile-bharosa hasti , Abdullah Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne. ye Hasan ki hadis ke alfaz hain aur ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik geelii ( nai ( qabr ke paas tashrif le gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par Namaz ( janaaza ( padhi aur unhon-ne ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey safain banaaein aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char takbeerein kahin . maine Aamir (bin-Sharaheel Shabi ( se puchha : aapko (ye hadis) kis ne bayan ki? unhon-ne kaha : aik qaabile-bharosa hasti jo us janazey mein Sharik they Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
2212,"Hushaim , abdul-Wahid-bin-Ziyad , Jareer, Sufiyan , Muaaz-bin-Muaaz aur Shoba sab ne Shebani se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki aur unmein se kisi ki riwayat mein nahi hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par char takbeerein kahin ."
2213,"Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid aur abu-Haseen ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ke qabr par Namaz padhney ke barey mein Shebani ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, unki hadis main ( bhi) ( وكبر اربعا ( (aap ne char takbeerein kahin (ke alfaz nahi hain."
2214,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik qabr par namaaze-janaaza padhi.
2215,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik siyah faam aurat masjid mein jhaado diya karti thi. ya aik naujawaan tha. padhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey na paya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat . ya us mard . ke barey mein puchha to logon ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : wo faut ho gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum logon ko mujhey itlaa nahi deni chahiye thi? kaha : maano un logon ne us aurat . ya us mard . ke mamley ko maamooli khayal kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey uski qabr dikhao . sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski qabr dikhai . to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski namaaze-janaaza padhi, phir farmaya : ahale quboor ke liye ye qabrein taareeki (andherey) se bhari hui hain aur meri un par Namaz padhney ki wjah se Allah Taala unke liye un ( qabron ( ko munawwar farma deta hai."
2216,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Lela ne kaha : Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-arqam ( hamarey janaazon par char takbeerein kaha kartey they, unhon-ne aik janazey par panch takbeerein kahin , maine unse (iske barey mein) puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kabhi-kabhi ( itni ( panch ( takbeerein kaha kartey they."
2217,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aamir-bin-Rabee'a (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum janazey ko dekho to uske liye khadey ho jaun yahan tak ke wo tum ko peechhey chhod de ( aagey nikal jaey) ya usey rakh diya jaey."
2218,"Leis aur Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki hai aur Yunus ki hadis mein hai ke unhon ( Aamir-bin-Rabiaa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. (usi tarah) Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne- Rumeh ne Leis se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Hazrat Aamir-bin-Rabiaa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs janazey ko dekhey , to agar wo janazey ke sath chal nahi raha, to khada ho jaey yahan tak ke wo ( janaaza ( usko peechhey chhod de ya usko peechhey chhodney se pahley usko rakh diya jaey."
2219,"Ayub , Ubaidullah , Ibne-Aun aur ibne-Juraij sab ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath Lais-bin-Sad ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, albatta ibne-Juraij ki hadis ye hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi janazey ko dekhey to agar wo iske peechhey ( saath) chalney wala nahi. to usko dekhtey hi khada ho jaey yahan tak ke wo usko peechhey chhod jaey."
2220,"Abu-Saleh ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum kisi janazey ke peechhey ( saath) jao to na baitho yahan tak ke usko rakh diya jaey."
2221,abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum janazey ko dekho to khadey ho jao aur jo shakhs janazey ke peechhey (saath) jaey to wo na baithey yahan tak ke us ( janazey ( ko rakh diya jaey.
2222,"Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik janaaza guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske liye khadey ho gaey aur ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khadey ho gaey phir ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ye to aik Yahudi aurat (ka janaaza ( hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maut khof aur ghabraahat (ka baais ( hai, to jab tum janazey ko dekho to khadey ho jao."
2223,"Muhammad-bin-Raafe ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik janazey ke liye jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se guzra khadey ho gaey, yahan tak ke wo ( nigahon se) ojhal ho gaya."
2224,"ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne ye khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huey suna, wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik janazey ke liye jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se guzra khadey ho gaey, yahan tak ke wo ( nigahon se) ojhal ho gaya."
2225,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se aur unhon-ne ibne-abi-Lela se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Qais-bin-Sad aur Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) qaadsiya main ( muqeem ( they ke unke paas se aik janaaza guzra to wo donon khadey ho gaey is par un donon se kaha gaya ke wo isi zamin (ke zimmii ( logon mein se hai to un donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se aik janaaza guzra to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : ye to Yahudi (ka janaaza ( hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya ye aik jaan nahi !?"
2226,Aamash ne Amr-bin-Murra se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur is mein hai : un donon ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke hamarey samney se aik janaaza guzra.
2227,"Leis ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne  waqid-bin-Amr-bin-Sad-bin-Muaz se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Naafe-bin-Juber ne mujhey khadey honey ki haalat mein dekha jabke ham aik janazey mein Sharik they aur wo khud baith kar janazey ko rakh diye janey ka intizar kar rahe they. to unhon-ne mujhey kaha : tumhen kis cheez ne khada kar rakha hai? maine kaha : main intizar kar raha hun ke janaaza rakh diya jaey kyonke Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) (uskey barey mein) hadis bayan kartey hain. to Naafe ne kaha : mujhey Masood-bin-Hakam ne Hazrat Ali-ibne- abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( shuruaat mein janaazon ke liye) khadey huey, phir ( baad mein) baithtey rahe."
2228,"( abdui Wahab ( ne kaha maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna, kaha : mujhey waqid bin-Amr-bin-Sad-bin-Muaz Ansari ne khabar di ke Naafe-bin-Juber ne unko khabar di ke unko Masood bin-Hakam Ansari ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo janaazon ke barey mein kehtey they : (pahley ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey hotey they ( baad mein) baithey rahtey aur unhon ( Naafe ( ne ye riwayat isliye bayan ki ke Naafe-bin-Juber ne waqid-bin-Amr ko dekha wo janazey ke rakh diye janey tak khadey rahe."
2229,ibne-abi-Zayda ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki.
2230,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Munkadir se hadis sunai, kaha : maine Masood-bin-Hakam se suna, wo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey to ham bhi khadey huey aur aap baithney lagey to ham bhi baithney lagey, yani janazey mein."
2231,Yahya qattaan ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
2232,"ibne-Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne Habib-bin-Ubaid se khabar di, unhon-ne us hadis ko Jubair-bin-Nufair se suna, wo kehtey they : maine Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik janaaza padhaayaa to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua mein se ye yad kar liya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : aey Allah ! usey bakhsh de is par raham farma aur usey aafiyat de, usey maaf farma aur uski baa-izzat ziyaafat (mehmaan nawazi) farma aur uske dakhil honey ki jagah ( qabr ( ko wasee farma aur us (ke gunahon ( ko pani , barf aur olon se dho de. usey gunahon se is tarah saaf kar de jis tarah tu ney safaid kapdey ko mail kuchail se saaf kiya aur usey us ghar ke badley mein behtar ghar , iske ghar walon ke badley mein behtar ghar waley aur uski biwi ke badley mein behtar biwi ata farma aur usko jannat mein dakhil farma aur qabr ke azab se aur aag ke azab se apni panah ata farmaa. kaha : yahan tak hua ke mere dil mein aarzoo paida hui ke ye maiyat mein hota ! (Muaawiya ne) kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Juber ne hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( Habib-bin-Ubaid ki) usi hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
2233,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne donon mein se har aik sanad ke sath ibne- Wahab ki hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki.
2234,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Jubair-bin-Nufair ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik janaaza padhaayaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : aey Allah ! usey bakhsh de is par raham farma aur usey aafiyat de, usey maaf farma aur uski baa-izzat ziyaafat farma aur uske dakhil honey ki jagah ( qabr ( ko wasee farma aur us (ke gunahon ( ko pani , barf aur olon se dho de, usey gunahon se is tarah saaf kar de jis tarah tu ney safaid kapdey ko mail kuchail se saaf kiya aur usey us ghar ke badley mein behtar ghar , iske ghar walon ke badley mein behtar ghar waley aur uski biwi ke badley mein behtar biwi ata farma aur usko jannat mein dakhil farma aur qabr ke azab se aur aag ke azab se apni panah ata farmaa. Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is maiyat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki duaon ki wjah se maine tamanna ki ke kash! wo maiyat mein hota !"
2235,"Abdul-Waris-bin-Saeed ne Husain-bin-Zakwan se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Barida ne Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umme-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaaze-janaaza padhai jo haalat nifaas mein wafat pa gain thin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki namaaze-janaaza ada karne ke liye iske ( samney ( darmyan mein khadey huey."
2236,"ibne-Mubarak , Yazid-bin-Harun aur fazal-bin-Musa sab ne Husain se usi (pichhli (sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki aur unhon-ne umme-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) (ka naam ( zikr nahi kiya."
2237,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Aqba-bin-mukarram-ammiyii ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi-Adi ne Husain (bin-Zakwan) se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Barida se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein nau-umr ladka tha aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( hadisey sun kar) yad kiya karta tha aur mujhey baat karne se iske siwa koi cheez na rokti ke yahan bahut log hain jo umr mein mujh se badey hain. maine rasool akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein aik aurat ki namaaze-janaaza ada ki jo haalate-nifaas mein wafat pa gain thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein iske ( samney ( darmyan mein khadey huey they. ibne- Musanna ki riwayat mein hai) Husain ne) kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Barida ne hadis sunai aur kaha : aap uski namaaze-janaaza ada karne ke liye iske ( samney ( darmyan mein khadey huey they."
2238,"Maalik-bin-Mighwal ne Samak-bin-Harab se aur unhon-ne Jaabir-bin-samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( baghair zeen ke) nangii pusht wala aik ghoda laya gaya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ibne- dah'daah (Raziallahu anhu) ke janazey se lautey to is par Sawar ho gaey jabke ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ird gird ( paidal ( chal rahe they."
2239,"Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se aur unhon-ne Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne- dah'daah (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaaze-janaaza padhai , phir nangii pusht wala ( baghair zeen ke) aik ghoda laya gaya, aik aadmi ne usey ( pakad kar) rokaa to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par Sawar ho gaey. wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko utha kar dil ki chaal chalney laga. ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey tez qadmon ke sath chal rahe they, kaha : logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne- dah'daah (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye jannat mein kitney latkey huey. padhi. ya jhukey huey. padhi. khoshey hain ! ya Shoba ne ( ibne- dah'daah (Raziallahu anhu) ke bajaey) abu dah'daah (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye kaha."
2240,"Aamir-bin-Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni us bimari ke doran mein jis mein wo faut ho gaey they, (apne haqdaar se) kaha : mere liye lahad taiyaar karna aur mere uper achchhey tareeqey se kachchi iinetein lagaanaa jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki qabr Mubarak (ke sath kiya gaya tha."
2241,"abu jamara ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qabr mein surkh motii chadar rakhi ( bichhaaii ( gaee thi. Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : abu jamara ka naam Nasar-bin-Imran aur abu-Tayyah ka naam Yazeed-bin-Humaid hai. (unka naam sanad mein nahi ( ye aik zayed fayda hai jiska izafa Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne ghaaliban kisi shagird ke sawal par kiya ( un donon ne sarkhas mein wafat paai."
2242,"samaama-bin-shafii ne bayan kiya, kaha : ham sarzameen Rome (mojooda Itly) ke jazeera rodas (RHODES) mein fazaala-bin-Ubaid ( aosii  Ansari ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they ke hamara aik dost wafat pa gaya. Hazrat fazaala-bin-Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki qabr ke barey mein hukm diya to usko barabar kar diya gaya, phir unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un ( qabron ( ko) zamin ke) barabar karne ka hukm detey they."
2243,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Habib-bin-abi-Sabit se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne abu-hayyaj Asadi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : kya main tumhen us ( muhim ( par rawaana na karun jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey rawaana kiya tha? (wo ye hai) ke tum kisi tasweer ya mujassamey ko na chhodnaa magar usey mitaa dena aur kisi buland qabr ko na chhodnaa magar usey ( zamin ke) barabar kar dena."
2244,Yahya qattan ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Habib se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne ( (لا تدع تمثالا الا طمسته ) ke bajaey) (ولا صورة الا طمستها ) (koii tasweer na chhodnaa magar usey mitaa dena ( kaha hai.
2245,"Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne ibne-Juraij se, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is baat se) mana farmaya ke qabr par choonaa lagaya jaey aur is par betha jaey aur is par Imaarat banai jaey."
2246,"Hajjaj-bin-Muhammad aur Abdur-Razzaq ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. padhi. aagey us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hai."
2247,"Ayub ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : qabron ko choona lagaaney se mana kiya gaya hai."
2248,"Jarir ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi angaarey par (is tarah) baith jaey ke wo iske kapdon ko jalaa kar uski jild tak pahunch jaey, iske haq mein us se behtar hai ke wo kisi qabr par baithey."
2249,Abdul-Azeez aur Sufiyan donon ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat bayan ki.
2250,"Basar-bin-Ubaidullah ne Hazrat Wasila (bin-Isqaa'-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-murtad ghanwii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qabron par na baitho aur na unki taraf ( rukh karke ( Namaz padho ."
2251,"abu-Idrees Kholani ne Hazrat Wasila-bin-Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-mursad-ghanwii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : qabron ki taraf ( rukh karke ( Namaz na padho aur na un par baitho ."
2252,Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad ne abdul-Wahid-bin-Hamza se aur unhon-ne Ibad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne hukm diya ke Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaaza masjid mein se guzara jaey (taake ( wo bhi unka janaaza ada kar sakein . aap ki baat par logon ne aetraz kiya to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : log kis qadr jald bhool gaey ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Badri sahabi ( Suhail-bin-baizaa (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaaze-janaaza masjid hi mein ada ki thi.
2253,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne abdul-Wahid se aur unhon-ne Ibad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki, wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kartey hain ke jab Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyon ne paigham bheja ke unke janazey ko masjid mein se guzaar kar ley jayen taake wo bhi unki namaaze-janaaza ada kar sakein to unhon ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne aisa hi kiya, us janazey ko unke hujron ke samney rok ( kar rakh ( diya gaya (taake ( wo namaaze-janaaza padh lein. ( phir (us ( janazey ( ko baabul janaiz se, jo maqaaid ki taraf ( khultaa ( tha, bahar nikala gaya. iske baad un ( beeviyon ( ko ye baat pahunchi ke logon ne ma'yoob (aibdaar) samjha hai aur kaha hai : janaazon ko masjid mein nahi laya jata tha. ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) tak pahunchi to unhon-ne farmaya : logon ne us kaam ko ma'yoob samajhney mein kitni jaldi ki jiska unhein ilm nahi ! unhon-ne hamari is baat par aetraz kiya hai ke janaaza masjid mein laya jaey, halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Suhail-bin-baizaa (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaaza masjid ke andar hi padha tha."
2254,"Hazrat abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke jab Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : unko masjid mein lao taake main bhi unki namaaze-janaaza ada kar sakoon. unki is baat par aetraz kiya gaya to unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baizaa ke do beton Suhel aur uske bhai (Sahal) (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaaza masjid main hi padha tha. Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Suhail-bin-da'd, jo ibne- baizaa hai, uski maan baizaa thin. (baizaa ka asl naam da'd tha, Suhel ke walid ka naam Wahab-bin-Rabee tha, usey sharf sohbat hasil na hua.)"
2255,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi , Yahya-bin-Ayub aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis sunai. padhi. Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein khabar di aur doosrey donon ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai. padhi. Ismail-bin-Jafar ne Sharik se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne kaha : . jis raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baari unke paas hoti to . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke aakhiri hissey mein Baqee (ke qabristaan mein) tashrif ley jatey aur farmatey : aey eman rakhney wali qaum ke gharaaney ! tum par Allah ki salamati ho, kal ke barey main tum se jiska wada kiya jata tha, wo tum tak pahunch gaya. tum ko (qiyamat ( tak mohlat de di gaee aur ham bhi, agar Allah ne chaha tum se milney waley hain. aey Allah ! Baqee gharqad (main rehney ( walon ko bakhsh de. Quteba ne (apni riwayat ( mein (tum tak pahunch gaya) nahi kaha, padhi."
2256,"Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne hamein hadis sunai aur kaha : ibne-Juraij ne Abdullah-bin-kaseer-bin-muttalib se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Qais-bin-Makhrima-bin-muttalib  ko kehtey huey suna ke maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahi thin, unhon-ne kaha : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur apni taraf se hadis na sunaun? ham ne kaha : kyon nahi. padhi. aur Hajjaj-bin Muhammad ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis sunai, kaha : Quraish ke aik fard Abdullah ne Muhammad-bin-Qais-bin-Makhrima-bin-muttalib se riwayat ki ke aik din unhon-ne kaha : kya main tumhen apni aur apni maa ki taraf se hadis na sunaun ? kaha : ham ne samjha ke unki murad apni us maan se hai jisne unhein janm diya ( lekin unhon-ne ( kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen apni taraf se aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se hadis na sunaun ? ham ne kaha : kyon nahi ! kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : (eik baar ( jab meri ( baari ki) raat hui jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahaan they, aap (masjid se) lautey , apni chadar (sarhaaney ( rakhi , apne donon jootey utaar kar apne donon paon ke paas rakhey aur apne tehband ka aik hissey bistar par bichhaayaa , phir let gaey. aap ne sirf itni der intizar kiya ke aap ne khayal kiya main so gaee hon, to aap ne aahista se apni chadar uthai , aahista se apne jootey pahney aur aahista se darwaza khola , nikley, phir aahista se usko band kar diya. (ye dekh kar) maine bhi apni qamees sar se guzari ( jaldi se pehni ( apna dupatta odha aur apni kamarband ( kamar par) baandhii , phir aap ke peechhey chal padi yahan tak ke aap Baqee (ke qabristaan mein) pahunchey aur khadey ho gaey aur aap lambi der tak khadey rahe, phir aap ne teen baar hath uthaey , phir aap paltey aur main bhi wapas lautii , aap tez ho gaey to main bhi tez ho gaee, aap tez tar ho gaey to main bhi tez tar ho gaee. aap daud kar chaley to maine bhi daudnaa shuru kar diya. main aap se aagey nikal aai aur ghar mein dakhil ho gaee. junhii main leti Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi ghar mein dakhil ho gaey aur farmaya : Aaisha ! tumhen kya hua kanp rahi ho? saans chadhi hui hai. maine kaha koi baat nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mujhey bataao gii ya phir wo mujhey bataaeyga jo lateef w khabeer hai) baareek been hai aur intihai ba-khabar ( hai. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon ! aur maine ( poori baat ( aapko bata di. aap ne farmaya : to wo siyah ( heulaa ( jo maine apne aagey dekha tha, tum thin ? maine kaha : haan. aap ne mere seeney ko zor se dhakelaa jis se mujhey takleef hui. phir aap ne farmaya : kya tum ne ye khayal kiya ke Allah tum par zyadti karega aur uska rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)? (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : log (kisi baat ko) kitna hi chipa lein Allah usko janta hai, haan. aap ne farmaya : jab tu ney (mujhey jatey huey) dekha tha us waqt Jibreel (Alaihissalam) mere paas aaey they. unhon-ne ( aa kar) mujhey awaz di aur apni awaz ko tum se makhfi (chipa) rakha , maine unko jawab diya to maine bhi tum se usko makhfi rakha aur wo tumharey paas andar nahi aa saktey they tum kapdey utaar chukein thin aur maine khayal kiya ke tum so chuki ho to maine tumhen bedaar karna munasib na samjha aur mujhey khadsha (dar) mehsus hua ke tum ( akelii ( wahshat mehsus karogii . to unhon ( Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ( ne kaha : aap ka rab aapko hukm deta hai ke aap ahale Baqee ke paas jayen aur unke liye bakhshish ki dua karein. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main unke haq main ( dua ke liye) kaisey kahun ? aap ne farmaya : tum kaho , mominon aur musalmanon mein se un thikaanon mein rehney walon par salamati ho, Allah Taala ham se aagey janey walon aur baad mein aaney walon par raham karey, aur ham insha-Allah zaroor tumharey sath milney waley hain."
2257,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Abdullah Asadi ne Sufiyan se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Alqama bin-Marsad se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Barida Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab wo qabristaan jatey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unko taleem diya kartey they, to ( seekhney ke baad) unka kehney wala kehta : Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : salamati ho musalmanon aur mominon ke thikaanon mein rehney walon par aur Zuhair ki riwayat mein hai : musalmanon aur mominon ke thikaaney mein rehney waalo tum par. padhi. aur ham insha-Allah zaroor ( tumharey saath) milney waley hain, main Allah Taala se apne aur tumharey liye aafiyat mangta hun."
2258,"Marwan-bin-Muawiya ne Yazeed , yani ibne- kaisaan se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apne rab se apni maa ke istighfar ki ijazat mangi to usne mujhey ijazat nahi di aur maine us se unki qabr ki ziyaarat ki ijazat mangi to mujhey ijazat de di."
2259,"Muhammad-bin-Ubaid ne Yazeed-bin-kaisaan se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni maa ki qabr ki ziyaarat ki, aap roey aur apne ird-gird walon ko bhi rulaayaa , phir farmaya : maine apne rab se ijazat mangi ke main unke liye bakhshish ki talab karun to mujhey ijazat nahi di gaee aur maine ijazat mangi ke main unki qabr ki ziyaarat karun to usne mujhey ijazat de di, to tum bhi qabron ki ziyaarat kiya karo kyonke wo tumhen maut ki yad dilaatii hain."
2260,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne hamein hadis sunai.  alfaz Abu-Bakar aur ibne-Numair ke hain.  unhon-ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne abu-Sanan se, jo zaraar-bin-Murra hain, hadis sunai, unhon-ne Maharib-bin-Disaar se, unhon-ne ibne-bareeda se, aur unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Barida-bin-Hasib Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat se mana kiya tha to ( ab ( tum unki ziyaarat kiya karo aur maine tumhen teen din se uper qurbaniyon ke gosht ( rakhney ( se mana kiya tha ( ab ( tum jab tak chaho rakh saktey ho aur maine tumhen mishkezon ke siwa kisi aur bartan mein nabeez peeney se mana kiya tha, ab tum har qism ke bartanon mein se pi saktey ho lekin koi nasha aawar cheez na piyo . ibne-Numair ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Abdullah-bin-Barida se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki. ( unhon-ne ibne-bareeda ke naam , Abdullah ki sarahat ki.)"
2261,"abu khaisma ne zubaid-al-yaami se, unhon-ne Maharib-bin-Disaar se, unhon-ne ibne-bareeda se, unhon-ne , mera khayal hai apne walid se, shak abu-khaisma ki taraf se hai.  aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. (usi tarah) Sufiyan ne Alqama-bin-Marsad se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. (usi tarah) Mamar ne ata khuraasaanii se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Barida ne apne walid se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. un sab ( Zubeda , Sufiyan aur Mamar ( ne abu Sanan ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
2262,"Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aadmi laya gaya jisne apne aapko aik chaudey teer se qatl kar daala tha to aap ne ( khud ( uski namaaze-janaaza nahi padhi. ( dusron ko padhney ka hukm diya jis tarah shuruaat mein aap dusron ko maqrooz ka janaaza padhney ka hukm detey they. ("
